// Copy this to `Signing.local.xcconfig` (same folder) and set your Team ID.
// That copy is git-ignored, so it's never committed and survives both a fresh
// clone and `xcodegen generate` — set it once and you never re-enter the team.
//
//     cp ios/Signing.local.xcconfig.example ios/Signing.local.xcconfig
//
// Find your Team ID in Xcode ▸ Settings ▸ Accounts ▸ (your team), or at
// developer.apple.com ▸ Membership.

DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID
